extends layout

block content
  #about
    .about-wrapper
      h1(style="text-align: center; font-size: 38px; color: #ff4b91; margin-bottom: 10px;") About My Dance Academy
      p.tagline(style="text-align: center; font-size: 20px; color: #ccc; margin-bottom: 40px;") Where passion meets rhythm.

      .about-box
        p(style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; color: #eee; margin-bottom: 20px;")
          | At 
          span(style="color: #ff6b6b; font-weight: bold;") My Dance Academy
          | , we believe dance is more than just movement — it's a celebration of expression, energy, and emotion. Founded with the vision to make dance accessible to all, we provide a vibrant space where beginners and pros alike can grow, perform, and shine.

        p(style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; color: #eee; margin-bottom: 20px;")
          | From 
          span(style="color: #ffb347; font-weight: bold;") Classical 
          | to 
          span(style="color: #7fd1b9; font-weight: bold;") Contemporary
          | , 
          span(style="color: #ff4b91; font-weight: bold;") Hip-Hop 
          | to 
          span(style="color: #ffd700; font-weight: bold;") Salsa 
          | — our expert instructors blend technique with creativity, helping each student find their unique style and confidence.

        p(style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; color: #eee;")
          | Join us — and let your story 
          span(style="color: #ff6b6b; font-style: italic;") move to music
          | .
